import {Card, Container, Grid, TextField, Typography} from '@material-ui/core'
import React from "react";
const Login = () =>{
    return(
        <Container>
            <Grid container justify="center">
                <Grid item lg={5} md={6}>
                    <Card align="center">
                        <Typography variant='h5' color='primary'>Ingrese su usuario</Typography>
                        <form>
                            <Grid container spacing={2}>
                                <Grid item xs={12}>
                                    <TextField
                                        label="Email"
                                        variant='outlined'
                                        fullWidth
                                        type='email'
                                    />
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12}>
                                    <TextField
                                        label="Password"
                                        variant='outlined'
                                        fullWidth
                                        type='password'
                                    />
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid>
                                    
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </form>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
    );
};
export default Login
